    <h2>Recent Projects</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Here are some of the digital experiences I've built recently.</p>

    <div class="projects-grid">

        <!-- PROJECT 1 -->
        <div class="project-card">
            <img src="~/Images/kookies.png" />
            <h3>Kookie – E-commerce Website</h3>
            <p>A clean and modern cake shop e-commerce site with cart, product pages, and checkout UI.</p>
            <a href="#" class="project-link">Live Demo</a>
        </div>

           <!-- PROJECT 2 -->
        <div class="project-card">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x250?text=Hangman+App" />
            <h3>Halloween Hangman (Mobile App)</h3>
            <p>A spooky-themed Hangman game built with mobile UI workflows and animations.</p>
            <a href="#" class="project-link">View App Screenshots</a>
        </div>

        <!-- PROJECT 3 -->
        <div class="project-card">
            <img src="~/Images/reboot.png" />
            <h3>Reboot Gadget(Figma)</h3>
            <p>explain that its an ecommerce product for 2nd hand devices. using figma with i forgot the term but its like you can move and click elements?</p>
            <a href="#" class="project-link">Try the Game</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-btn">
        <a href="/Portfolio" class="btn-secondary">View All Projects</a>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- SHOP PREVIEW -->
<section class="shop-section">
    <h2>New in the Shop</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Pastel book-themed collectibles for design lovers.</p>

    <div class="shop-grid">
        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Product+1" />
            <h3>Book Lover Pin</h3>
            <p>$12</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Product+2" />
            <h3>"Chapter One" Sticker Pack</h3>
            <p>$8</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Product+3" />
            <h3>Pastel Bookmark Patch</h3>
            <p>$10</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-btn">
        <a href="/Shop" class="btn-secondary">Explore the Full Shop</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>
        I am a UI/UX Designer and Front-End Developer with a passion for pastel visuals,
        book-themed creations, and intuitive digital interfaces.
    </p>

    <div class="skills-list">
        <span>Figma</span>
        <span>HTML/CSS</span>
        <span>JavaScript</span>
        <span>C# ASP.NET Core</span>
        <span>Responsive Design</span>
        <span>Wireframing</span>
    </div>
</section>
